RCP 2.6

One sentence about RCP 6.0 Below you can view the absolute and relative change maps. Check the Map Description for information about the creation of the map, especially the creation of the bins. Below the maps you can download a high resolution pdf for each map.

Absolute Change under RCP 6.0

However, cells that have a lot of agricultural production will exhibit large absolute changes even under small relative changes and vice versa. Therefore it is important to simultaneously take the growth rate into account.
